# - **Cluster 1**: Low income, low spending – Low priority customers  
# - **Cluster 2**: High income, low spending – Upsell opportunity  
# - **Cluster 3**: Low income, high spending – Discount-driven customers  
# - **Cluster 4**: Average income and spending – Regular customers
